nodes.text: The Jeodu were a tall, brown-skinned species. Their heads were topped with a conical white crystal; for this reason, the name "Dequc" (meaning "Whitehead") was common among them. A Jeodu, Dequc became the leader of Black Nebula in 3.5 ABY, in an attempt to resurrect the Black Sun criminal organization, and many Jeodu joined the organization.
Besides Dequc, other Jeodu included Eoodso, Traff, Chackra, and Clomv.
